cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.LO, cs.CL, cs.CR 

This paper deals with reasoning and repairing inconsistent knowledge bases, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the relationship between optimal repairs and argumentation frameworks, which falls under computational logic (cs.LO) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). Finally, the paper touches upon preference-based argumentation frameworks, which is a topic in cryptography and security (cs.CR).
